snippet.title: Amber Heard may still be driving Tesla Elon Musk gave her while they were dating | Fox Business
snippet.description:
#SpaceX 
https://www.foxbusiness.com/entertainment/amber-heard-seemingly-spotted-driving-tesla-that-elon-musk-gave-her-while-they-were-dating
Shortly after her tumultuous marriage to Johnny Depp ended in 2017, Heard and the SpaceX CEO made their relationship public.While no one expected her to give up the car just because her relationship with Musk ended in 2017, it is surprising that she feels comfortable driving it given that it was previously reported that she believed it was bugged with a listening device by the billionaire while they were dating.
